{"tid":1429437,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[民間記者會]第二次可以說這句話嗎?","createTime":"2019-08-07T13:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T18:46:07.000Z","uid":267959,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb31f100ae8539f53de99893abd758bd5f30ab1","tid":1429437,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:34:46.000Z","msg":"這是在8月5號前柯士甸站出口前的照片:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2q3h1Cw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2q3h1Cw.jpg&h=377f4c04&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n這是在8月6號返工時﹕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VWUw54t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVWUw54t.jpg&h=5852287e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n因只隔了一日，而且這裏連連儂牆都不算是，應該是普通市民做的。自8月5日後感覺本身中間派或對政事泠感的人對我們都有點攻擊性傾向<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我想原因可能出在對當天真的有需要出行的人受到阻礙，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">我知道各巴打在不合作運動時有不停對市民說對不起</span></strong>。但主流媒體不會播放這些片段<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。所以可以在第二次民間記者會對公眾說句，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對不住</span></span></strong></span>嗎?<br />\n以下是我考慮到若說對不住的好處﹕<br />\n1. 我們不是如CCTV所報的無理，我們是清楚自己所做的事，知道對市民造成困擾。可能的話扭轉一些市民對我們的形象<br />\n2. 平息8月5日後的民憤<br />\n<br />\n借鏡777的道歉表現，若道歉以最大誠懇但又不能過份誇張的方式，我是<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建議</span></span>可以的話就:<br />\n1. &quot;我們對，在罷工日要上班或出行的市民 所造成的困擾 感到非常對唔住&quot;<br />\n2. 鞠躬十幾秒  (對不起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />需要出現在記者會上的巴打)<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以討論一下<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">要不要</span></span>說對不起跟它的利<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">與弊</span></span>"},{"pid":"184795c6b2df47b02e2387630223e580cdc37450","tid":1429437,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:35:26.000Z","msg":"多咗好多人買雷射筆，求推Post: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【極重要】請立即停止漫罵及用雷射筆射向拍照的途人/大廈單位<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418134</a>"},{"pid":"b7b48a5d27f1cf613d36d2cf4f9a7376522e4092","tid":1429437,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:40:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a44ed591763f02400d1137d11fee0c8577e0718","tid":1429437,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:54:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1180d55fc4884df244f232532a54088a9e29f0d","tid":1429437,"uid":37686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:56:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"406040fa5c573135545d19f504555de6f7924765","tid":1429437,"uid":231583,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:00:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得道歉唔係問題，但一定係強調政府零回應別無他法先咁做，個罪魁禍首依然係政府"},{"pid":"009ba262e168984397567c800cd18963ab19a63a","tid":1429437,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:03:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74b9e56bf6edd4e03fac4c66c84f6ba7eabdfb97","tid":1429437,"uid":77202,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:09:20.000Z","msg":"道你老味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3184ef96d5e957a3f59085b765f36ace0e945cb3","tid":1429437,"uid":77202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:09:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25d722297581844de98204c6f42717fd1476c3e8","tid":1429437,"uid":77202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:09:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"14ac68d6625f29b1ab3ff01680ebbbe54008177d","tid":1429437,"uid":288876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:26:21.000Z","msg":"要解釋清楚我地點比